“三月赏樱唯有武大。
"Only Wu Da wins in March.
”武大的樱花一向是武汉初春的胜景，一般始于3月中旬，历时2到3周。
The cherry blossoms, which usually start in mid-March and last for two to three weeks, have always been a hit in Wuhan early spring.
每到那时，数万名游客蜂拥而至，然而由于今年新冠肺炎疫情的暴发，无论是本地的居民，还是外地的游客，都无缘于此。
Tens of thousands of tourists flock to the city each year, but neither locals nor tourists from the outside world have benefited from the outbreak this year.
基于这样的情况，3月12日，武汉大学发布《武汉大学关于加强2020年樱花开放期间实行校园封闭管理的通告》，宣布为满足师生员工、校友以及社会公众赏樱需求，武汉大学樱花盛花期免费开放10天左右网络“云赏樱”通道。
In response to this situation, Wuhan University on March 12 issued a notice on strengthening the closed management of campuses during the 2020 cherry blossoms opening period, announcing that to meet the demand of teachers and students, alumni and the public at large, Wuhan University cherry blossoms will be open for free for about 10 days.
根据新华社报道，中国移动咪咕全程提供5G＋VR直播技术支持，是全球首次5G+VR“云赏樱”。
According to Xinhua News Agency, China Mobile Mimi provides 5G + VR live technical support, the world's first 5G + VR "cloud reward."
截图来源：武汉大学官微3月16日上午10点，武大云赏樱刚一开播，1分钟的时间里，淘宝直播间里瞬间就涌入30万人，直接超过去年整个赏樱季的游客人数。
2007-9-25 21: 55 [hide] http: / / www.51education.net [/ url] www.51education.net) [/ center] [/ center] [/ center] [/ center] [/ center] [/ center] [/ center] [/ center]
目前，微博上“武汉大学云赏樱”这一话题的阅读量已经超过6600万次。
At present, the topic of "Wuhan University" has been read more than 66 million times.
5G，很明显是2020年“云赏樱”的关键词，而今年又被誉为是5G大发展的一年。
5G, apparently the keyword for the 2020 "cloud reward", has been hailed as a year of 5G growth.
2019年12月，由中国信通院等机构联合发布的《中国5G经济报告2020》显示，2020年，5G商用将在中国拉动投资9000亿元，创造54万人就业。
In December 2019, China's 5G Economic Report 2020, published jointly by the China Institute of Information and Communications Technology and others, showed that 5G business will boost investment in China by 900 billion yuan and create 540,000 jobs in 2020.
那么，5G云赏樱到底有什么特别？近万亿元投资的5G技术今年又能给国人带来什么呢？5G和“云”的爆发实际上，“云赏樱”并不是一个新的活动了。
So what's so special about 5 gigabytes of fuchsia? What can the nearly trillion-dollar 5G technology do this year to bring to the countrymen? 5G and Cloud Outbreak In fact, "cloud reward" is not a new activity.
随着直播和短视频的技术不断兴起，在2013年前后，包括“云赏樱”在内的多样化云旅游就已经悄然兴起，但只不过那时候还不是在利用5G技术，所以普及程度还不是很高。
With the rise of live and short-video technology, diversified cloud tourism, including cloud handouts, has sprung up around 2013, but it was only then that 5G technologies were not being used, so popularity was not high.
某资本方的投资经理陈吉（化名）对笔者表示，这次疫情的暴发，其实在一定程度上刺激了云经济的发展，因为对于很多旅游景点本身来说，选择云旅游的方式就是选择了一种新的“求生”方式，而这段时间，由于大家都不便出门，反而是一个好机会来发展这种模式，否则，等待着这些旅游景点的就是惨重的损失。
Chen Ji (alias), an investment manager at a capital firm, told the author that the outbreak had in fact spurred the cloud economy, because for many destinations themselves, cloud tourism was a new way of "survival," a good time to develop the model because everyone was too busy to go out.
“5G技术，可以看作是云旅游发展的催化剂。
"5G technology can be seen as a catalyst for cloud tourism.
”陈吉这样表述。
"Chen Ji said.
此前，3月5日，携程集团董事局主席梁建章在“旅游复兴V计划”线上发布会上公开表示：“旅行行业为全球贡献了超过10%的GDP，遗憾的是，在这次疫情中，旅行行业也是受损最严重的行业之一。
Earlier, on March 5, the chairman of Ctrip Group, Liang Jianzhang, said publicly at the online launch of the "V-Plan for Tourism Revival": "The travel industry contributes more than 10 per cent of the world's GDP. Unfortunately, the travel industry is also one of the hardest-hit industries in the epidemic.
”此前，根据同程旅游发布的《2020春节黄金周居民旅游消费趋势报告》预测，2020年春节黄金周出游人数预计在4.5亿人次左右。
The report, based on the 2020 Spring Festival Golden Week residents' travel consumption trend, predicted that around 450 million people would travel during the 2020 Spring Festival Golden Week.
相比2019年春节黄金周4.15亿人次出游贡献5139亿元的战绩，2020年春节黄金周消费总额将大概率突破5200亿元。
Compared to 2019 Spring Festival Golden Week 415 million excursions contributed 513.9 billion yuan of record, the 2020 Spring Festival Golden Week consumption will be a large probability of more than 520 billion yuan.
很明显，这份报告是发布于疫情暴发之前，如果这样来考虑，在疫情持续的近两个月时间里，旅游行业的损失是一个庞大的数字。
Clearly, the report comes before the outbreak, and if one considers it, the tourism industry's losses are enormous in the almost two months of the epidemic.
“因为这样的特殊时期，旅游行业的公司转向云旅游是可以理解的，而由于5G技术对于云旅游的赋能，其实一定程度上解决了不少传统单纯直播旅游的痛点，提升了观众体验。
"Because of these exceptional times, it is understandable that companies in the tourism industry are turning to cloud tourism, and the ability of 5G technology to cloud tourism has, in fact, solved some of the pain points of traditional live-only tourism and enhanced the audience experience.
”易唯思商务咨询的咨询顾问周启冉这样表示。
Zhou QiRan, a consultant for Yi Wei-si's business consultancy, said.
大唐移动5G产品线副总裁李文向笔者介绍，视频直播具有实时现况性质，互动性要求很高，而且视频的流畅性极为重要。
Li Wenwen, vice-president of product line of Datang Mobile 5G, told the author that live video broadcasting is real-time and highly interactive, and video fluency is extremely important.
而传统的直播很难保证视频流的传输成功率，容易出现丢帧、花屏、卡顿等问题。
But the traditional live broadcast can not guarantee the video stream transmission success rate, easy to lose frame, flower screen, Catton and so on.
全球顶级5G+8K转播车（图片来源：视觉中国）“与传统直播相比，5G+VR直播的形式具备全景、3D以及交互3个特点。
World Class 5G + 8K RV (Source: Visual China) "5G + VR Live Broadcast features panoramic, 3D and interactive features compared to traditional live broadcasting.
5G带来的超低延迟可以使设备提升全景视频的分辨率和码率，从而使VR视频达到更好的观看体验。
The ultra-low latency brought by 5G enables the device to improve the resolution and bit rate of panoramic video, thus enabling VR video to achieve a better viewing experience.
”李文这样表示。
"said Li Wen.
李文认为，5G直播将成为未来直播报道的主要方式，应用领域将会不仅仅局限于云旅游，还可以应用到演唱会、体育赛事、竞技等各种现场，同时，能为用户带来更真实、更具沉浸感的感官体验。
Li said the 5G live broadcast will be the main way to report live in the future. The application area will not only be limited to cloud tourism, but also be used in concerts, sports events and competitions.
文旅部产业发展司司长高政在18日的发布会上表示，随着抗击疫情形势的不断好转，广大群众的文旅消费热情也在不断地恢复和高涨。
As the situation of fighting the epidemic continues to improve, the enthusiasm of the general public for cultural and tourism consumption is also recovering and rising, Gao Zheng, Secretary for Industrial Development of the Ministry of Culture and Tourism, said at a press conference on the 18th.
下一步将围绕“有序开放、狠抓线上、帮扶企业”12个字推动文旅消费。
The next step will revolve around "orderly opening, hard-line, help enterprises" 12 words to promote the consumption of cultural tourism.
其中，“狠抓线上”就是要加快发展数字文旅产业，把握产业发展新趋势、新需求，推动文化旅游与数字经济深度融合。
Among them, "hard-line" is to accelerate the development of the digital tourism industry, grasp the new trends and needs of industrial development, promote cultural tourism and the deep integration of the digital economy.
这也就意味着，即使疫情过去了，随着5G等技术对旅游行业的赋能，云旅游在未来仍有一席之地。
This means that, even after the epidemic is over, cloud tourism will have a place in the future, thanks to the ability of technologies such as 5G to empower the tourism industry.
2020年的5G能带来什么？除了可以“云赏樱”，预计今年总投资近万亿元的5G技术还能带来什么？李文向笔者表示，今年是我国5G建设发展的关键之年，虽然疫情在一定程度上给5G建设带来了影响，但随着通信行业复产复工脚步加快，全年来看，我国整体5G建设将不会放缓。
What will the 5G be able to bring about in 2020? In addition to "reward the clouds," Li told the author that this year is a critical year for China's 5G construction. Although the epidemic has affected 5G construction to some extent, the overall 5G construction in China will not slow down over the course of the year.
据李文介绍，从总体上来看，国内三大运营商都立下“2020年5G建设目标不减”的军令状，预计55万个基站将在年底建成。
Overall, Li said, the country's three major operators have made "no less than the 2020 goal of 5G construction" military writ, 550,000 base stations are expected to be completed by the end of the year.
此外，三大运营商加大5G网络建设的同时，还正在布局5G独立组网，而相应的网络也会在今年底开始商用，对此中国移动已经计划四季度实现5G独立组网商用，建成全球规模最大的5G网络。
In addition, the three major operators are expanding their 5G networks and are laying out a 5G independent network, which will begin commercial operations by the end of this year. China Mobile has planned 5G independent networking in the fourth quarter, making it the world's largest 5G network.
MWC19上海展，5G网络 5G+（图片来源：视觉中国）至于5G技术的具体落地，除了视频直播，李文重点提到了智慧医疗、车联网、智慧教育和智慧工厂这4个方面。
As for the specific landing of 5G technology, in addition to the live video broadcast, Li highlighted four areas: smart medicine, car networking, smart education and intelligent factory.
以智慧医疗为例，5G可实现医院内外大量医疗设备互联、医疗大数据快速处理、医疗信息实时共享，极大地提高医疗工作效率，助力医疗资源脱离地域限制。
In the case of Smart Medicine, 5G enables the interconnection of a large number of medical devices in and outside hospitals, the rapid processing of large-scale medical data, and the real-time sharing of medical information.
例如2019年6月，大唐移动同湖北移动合作，将5G技术应用于远程医疗服务，支撑十堰市太和医院成功实现医联体内5G远程协同手术，远程指导神农架林区人民医院医生顺利完成腹腔镜下行胆囊切除手术操作、远程协同实施74岁老人膝关节手术等。
In June 2019, for example, Datang Mobile partnered with Hubei Mobile to apply 5G technology to telemedicine service, support Shiyan Taihe Hospital to successfully carry out 5G long-range cooperative surgery, remotely guide doctors of Shennongjia Forest People's Hospital to successfully complete laparoscopic cholecystectomy and long-range coordinated knee surgery for the 74-year-old.
但周启冉则提出一个担忧，他认为，如果说到5G技术真正要“落地”，2020年或许很难实现。
But Zhou Qiling has raised a concern that if the 5G technology is really going to land by 2020, it may be difficult to do so.
“因为普通的5G网络不行，延迟和网速都达不到预期，体验效果会很差，技术上要更进一步，大概还要1～3年去演进。
"Because normal 5G networks don't work, latency and network speeds are falling short of expectations, the experience is going to be bad, the technology is going even further, and it's going to take a year or so to evolve."
”李文还补充道，5G从提出需求到标准制定，再到相关设备形态成熟可商用化、实体应用逐渐落地，需要长达10年左右的发展时间。
Mr Levin adds that 5G takes up to 10 years to develop from demand to standard-setting to commercial and physical applications as the equipment matures.
而谁能更快抓住新一代技术为社会及产业赋能，谁就能占有更大优势。
And who can seize the new generation of technologies more quickly and empower society and industry will have a greater advantage?
“同样地，6G网络也需要相似甚至更长的时间发展。
"Similarly, 6G networks need to develop in a similar or even longer time.
而从现在开始研究6G，其实是在投资未来。
And to start looking at 6G now is to invest in the future.
”（编辑：黄玉璐 校对：颜京宁）推荐阅读点击大图|为什么美国要“直升机撒钱”？点击大图|钟南山：对输入病例要高度警惕，疫情传播第一波传染性很强！。
